# AI-generated assets (persist locally, don't commit to git).
# NOTE: `public/npc/*.png` is deliberately NOT ignored — the 5 canonical NPC
# portraits are committed into the repo along with a spritecook-assets.json
# manifest so a fresh clone of OpenClaw Quest ships with a usable tavern.
# Background tiles, generic sprites and icons stay local-only.
public/bg/*.png
public/sprites/*.png
public/icons/*.png
public/bg/backup-v1/
public/bg/originals/
public/sprites/originals/
public/npc/sprites/
public/items/raw/
public/skills/raw/
*.jiuguan.png

# Internal / tooling (not part of the product)
demo/
scripts/
REVIEW-LOG.md
PROJECT-CONTEXT.md
